            <title>[LU-19285] moves all direct calls from yaml_parser_delete() to yaml_parser_cleanup() and all direct calls from yaml_emitter_delete() to yaml_emitter_cleanup()</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19285</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This is a followup patch after commit ca6fdf73528a0 (&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19234&quot; title=&quot;memory leak when running lst utility&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-19234&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-19234&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;br/&gt;
This patch moves all direct calls from yaml_parser_delete()&lt;br/&gt;
to yaml_parser_cleanup() and all direct calls from&lt;br/&gt;
yaml_emitter_delete() to yaml_emitter_cleanup() wherever&lt;br/&gt;
possible.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
